tool_description: Astrology made easy! Astrological calculation, birth charts, composite charts in SVG. Plus all astrological data.
name: Astrologer
title: Astrologer

api_list.name: Current Date/Time: Get Data
api_list.description:
Returns the current astrological data in JSON format.

Response model:
* `status` - The status of the request.
* `data` - The data of the astrological subject.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://astrologer.p.rapidapi.com/api/v4/now"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "astrologer.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://astrologer.p.rapidapi.com/api/v4/now"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "astrologer.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
